Package io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api.worker.internal

Class CycleTasksManager

java.lang.Object
io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api.worker.internal.CycleTasksManager
public class CycleTasksManager extends Object
Manages the Read-, Write- and Wait-Tasks for one Cycle.

  • onBeforeProcessImage() initialize the next Cycle if previous Cycle had finished
  • onExecuteWrite() puts Write-Tasks as highest priority
